  <brief_title>Study of Motexafin Gadolinium and Docetaxel for Advanced Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Trial of Motexafin Gadolinium (MGd) and Docetaxel Chemotherapy in the Treatment of Advanced Solid Tumors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Pharmacyclics LLC.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Pharmacyclics LLC.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, side effects, and dosage for
      Motexafin Gadolinium given with the chemotherapy drug docetaxel to patients with advanced
      cancers. Secondly, tumor response to the combined treatment, drug levels in the body, and
      drug interactions will be evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
