  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Determine the Dose Limiting Toxicity at 8 weeks (2 cycles), and the Maximum Tolerated Dose at 24 weeks.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Tumor response rate 8, 16 and 24 weeks, and common PK parameters at 24 weeks</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
